{
  "texts": [
    "By framing the AES task as MIL, this work presented sentence annotation mechanism that can enhance the feedback process in building explainable AES model.",
    "Kumar and Boulanger (2020) proposed a deep learning approach to automated essay scoring, which provides feedback using explanation.",
    "The aim of the proposed approach is to predict the quality of the writing style and expose the decision process that led to these predictions.",
    "SHAP is utilized to to generate both local and global explanations.",
    "Fiacco et al. (2022) proposed a neural approach to automated Rhetorical Structure Theory (RST) parsing which can be used to provide structure level feedback by analyzing discourse structure of essays."
  ]
}